◇ Kasturi Setu (The Bridge Vault)
◇ Locks Pyar on KasturiChain and emits states for the Polygon Relayer

माना सेतु_निर्माता = "0xBridgeRelayerAddress"
माना सञ्चय = ०

कार्य सेतु_बन्धन(विदेशी_पता, मात्रा) {
    ◇ Lock native Pyar intended for Polygon WPYAR
    सञ्चय = सञ्चय + मात्रा
    
    ◇ Emits a log (in our sandbox, we can write to the output or rely on the transaction data itself for the relayer)
    √vac+ति·"LOCKED:" + यन्त्र_पता + ":" + प्रेषक + ":" + विदेशी_पता + ":" + मात्रा
    
    पुनरावृत्त सत्य
}

कार्य सेतु_मोचन(स्वदेशी_पता, मात्रा) {
    ◇ Unlock native Pyar. Only the authorized Bridge Relayer can call this!
    यदि (प्रेषक != सेतु_निर्माता) {
        √vac+ति·"अधिकार_नास्ति"
        पुनरावृत्त असत्य
    }
    
    यदि (सञ्चय < मात्रा) {
        √vac+ति·"अपर्याप्त_सञ्चय"
        पुनरावृत्त असत्य
    }
    
    सञ्चय = सञ्चय - मात्रा
    
    ◇ The actual transfer logic will be handled by the relayer initiating a zero-fee transfer from the vault,
    ◇ or the Setu contract triggers an internal transfer (if the engine supports contract outbound transfers).
    ◇ For Kasturi V1, the Relayer simply holds the keys to the Vault address and transfers out manually.
    
    √vac+ति·"UNLOCKED:" + स्वदेशी_पता + ":" + मात्रा
    पुनरावृत्त सत्य
}
